Our vessel pop-up drains will work with most vessel sink drain openings and can be opened or closed simply by pressing the top of the drain mechanism up or down. This type of drain enables you to fill the sink with water, but remember there is no overflow feature on most vessel sinks or these drains. These drains are available in chrome, brushed nickel, antique bronze, and oil rubbed bronze finishes.
